### Output Format

Produce a JSON array of port objects. Each port has these required fields:
- `element_type`: always "port"
- `port_id`: prefix `port_` + component ref + pin (e.g., `port_r1_1`, `port_u1_vcc`)
- `component_id`: must match a component_id from the list above
- `pin_number`: integer, starts at 1
- `name`: pin name (e.g., "1", "anode", "VCC", "GND")
- `electrical_type`: one of: power_in, power_out, signal, ground, passive, no_connect

